					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In my first NES game, Lan Master, I only needed four sprites for the cursor and decided to handle them with direct OAM writes, without using DMA. It worked well in emulators, but turned out to be glitchy on the hardware. So I had to change it to DMA.</div>

